<TEXT>
<P>
Actress Linda Hunt will make her Los Angeles stage debut in Emily Mann's 
one-woman drama, "Annulla," opening Oct. 21 at the Court Theatre in West 
Hollywood. Hunt, who won an Academy Award in 1983 for her performance in "The 
Year of Living Dangerously," will play the title role of a Holocaust survivor; 
playwright Mann (whose credits include "Execution of Justice," on the 1979 Dan 
White murder trial) will direct. Claudia Puig 
