More than half the men arrested in 14 major cities who volunteered for drug 
testing were found to have ingested at least one drug, the Justice Department 
said. The highest percentage of drug use, 82%, was discovered in Philadelphia, 
followed by San Diego with 80%, according to the Drug Use Forecasting study by 
