groups, meets at a Valley park. ; Photo, Jacket buttons feature bands Madness, 
the Specials, English Beat. ; Photo, 'The Nazis offered them a group. Now we're 
offering them a group on the other side.' -- Todd Schwartz, 21, West Coast 
coordinator of SHARP GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SKINHEADS AGAINST RACIAL PREJUDICE (ORGANIZATION); SKINHEADS; YOUTH; GANGS -- 
LOS ANGELES COUNTY; RACIAL RELATIONS -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
