Photo, Students sing and dance a routine to the musical "Annie" in theater 
class. Sean Nelson, right, of Huntington Beach relaxes between classes. ; 
Photo, Algebra students tackle a series of problems. Cookies went to the 
winner. ; Photo, Nicole Inouye, 13 GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
