<HEADLINE>
<P>
LAGUNA HILLS' KORTMAN PICKS SAN LUIS OBISPO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ron Kortman of Laguna Hills High School has signed a letter of intent to play 
baseball at Cal Poly San Luis Obispo. 
</P>
<P>
Kortman was 11-2 last season for the Hawks, who reached the Southern Section 
3-A quarterfinals. He had 53 strikeouts and a 0.89 earned-run average during 
the regular season. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASEBALL PLAYERS; ATHLETIC RECRUITING; CALIFORNIA POLYTECHNIC UNIVERSITY AT SAN 
LUIS OBISPO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
