<TEXT>
<P>
China's top leaders and generals today congratulated the army for suppressing 
June's pro-democracy demonstrations, but foreign ambassadors in Beijing 
protested by boycotting the Army Day celebrations. 
</P>
<P>
In a speech Defense Minister Gen. Qin Jiwei twice praised Deng Xiaoping in what 
appears to be a growing personality cult surrounding the 84-year-old senior 
leader. 
</P>
